[5] Cholera - Uganda (Rakai)
Date: Sun, 15 Oct 2006
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: New Vision [edited]
<http://www.newvision.co.ug/D/8/13/526813>

Cholera has killed 4 people in a week, the district director of health
services, Dr. Robert Mayanja, has said. Mayanja said the 4 people who died
on Thu and Fri, 12-13 Oct 2006 at Rakai hospital were residents of the town
council in the areas of Kibona and Byakabanda sub-county.
